1:32.000Z","msg":"抗戰勝利到解放個幾年，中國形勢影響全世界，點會好似19講到只係杜冇遠見咁簡單"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T06:41:39.000Z","msg":"咁點解釋當年美國由得中華民國敗走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T09:03:49.000Z","msg":"歐洲優先囉"},{"pid":"94c3dc8ed68035e2c69ff0ac6727ad06c2dd62d0","tid":869130,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T09:05:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N0WNmh8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN0WNmh8.gif&h=e8601f10&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}